{"tid":884917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務卿：中國是美國最大國家安全挑戰","createTime":"2018-11-01T03:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T09:13:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78e0c320e38c3795864c98f07c73e499a0ae068b","tid":884917,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國國務卿：中國是美國最大國家安全挑戰</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181101/1458161/?fbclid=IwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181101%2F1458161%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4&d=uXNkVBNXjWnhZA1iHhmX7Rxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=3aca4a08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181101%2F1458161%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4&h=0e6bceed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181101/1458161/?fbclid=IwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4</a><br />\n<br />\n美中對抗局面越來越清晰。繼美國副總統潘斯公開演說譴責中國後，美國國務卿龐皮歐昨日接受專訪時表示，中國是美國多年來面臨最大的國家安全挑戰，他還說美國正在努力說服中國，當個「正常國家」。<br />\n <br />\n[img]<span style=\"color: red;\">龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）昨日在「英格拉罕電台秀」（Laura Ingraham radio show）上表示，中國或許是美國面臨的最大國家安全挑戰，而川普政府正在從各個層面展開對抗。他說：「不讓中國取得半導體技術只是我們對抗中國的其中一部份。美國政府正多管齊下，並在川普總統的指示下，說服中國在商業上扮演正常國家角色，並遵守國際法律。」<br />\n </span>[/img]<br />\n同日在另一個廣播節目上，龐皮歐也再次提到中國的商業間諜惡行「極不妥當」、「和世界強權及全球領袖的身分不符」。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部前天起訴包括2名中國情報人員在內的10人，指控他們在2010至2015年間，串謀入侵美國及外國公司電腦系統，盜取敏感數據和渦輪扇引擎技術，讓中國公司不必研究和開發，就能造出相同或類似引擎。此為今年9月以來第3起中國情報人員遭美方起訴案件。美國副總統潘斯（Mike Pence）上月初發表演說，細數中國的不公平貿易作為、竊取商業機密與駭客攻擊美國網路，被視為冷戰後最嚴厲的對中演說。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"5e4586cc9d7a6abf6b81b6b5191aba5d34b8c863","tid":884917,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"中國係美國最大威脅，可惜中國最後成最大贏家"},{"pid":"cf04b359c94b5eaaed36a4b9961af90ac45ab2e4","tid":884917,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc972580e7e78ceffbdb18e0f38416211be48d35","tid":884917,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"美國突然咁淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccc85a1cf1281ece67dec9c1194a3b5ea48909f","tid":884917,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f87a0646eeefffe809aa81ea5386ce84b9c1d15","tid":884917,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"支那係一百倍極權版北韓"},{"pid":"a04c881346c2e7324eaedf7a41a0a3cc4a45ef9c","tid":884917,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0819ca1fc0a6150e28d816cdd248a853edab40","tid":884917,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"大紅龍"},{"pid":"82af5c15e69ffc3137a0aed6d447d5e87465d0ba","tid":884917,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf04b359c94b5eaaed36a4b9961af90ac45ab2e4","tid":884917,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"1e6c41d2a0b3102e9a820a7031183e0d703e3631","tid":884917,"uid":41963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc972580e7e78ceffbdb18e0f38416211be48d35","tid":884917,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"美國突然咁淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"